Basic Installation
==================

You shuold have wxWidgets installed on your distribution.
(libwxgtk2.8 and libwxgtk2.8-dev)
Make sure you have libxvidcore4 and livxvidcore4-dev
Download, compile and install revel library (http://revel.sourceforge.net)

Now you can compile wxCam:

Type:

shell> make

and copy bin/wxcam in your path (e.g. /usr/bin)
